name: Bluwhale
description: BluWhale is Web3’s Intelligence Layer — a consumer-powered decentralized AI network where developers and enterprises deploy AI agents to serve 3.6 million users with financial services. Backed by UOB Venture Management and SBI Holdings and integrated with chains including Sui, Arbitrum, Tezos, Cardano, and Movement Labs, BluWhale builds a multi-chain infrastructure for AI-driven financial intelligence. Its TGE on October 21 2025 introduces $BLUAI for gas fees, governance, staking, and node operations.
